The fact that you trust me and feel safe with me which allows you to be comfortable around me and share all your thoughts, has been one of those reasons why I started trusting you a lot more, because as far as I know, it's not easy for men to express themselves but you've done that with me ü•∫

And I really feel at ease, knowing that I am that important to you.ü•∫
